N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 91.20 - Continuation of procedures

State Regulations

For uniform traffic tickets issued prior to the effective
date of entry into the TSLE&D System, but disposed of subsequent to that
date, courts shall adhere to the procedures in effect at the time the ticket
was issued. Notes
